description_for_human: A warm, rustic neo-skeuomorphic CSS component library with 28 components and 4 themes.
description_for_model: DAUB is a CSS UI kit with 28 neo-skeuomorphic components and 4 themes (light, dark, grunge-light, grunge-dark). Use db-* class prefix. Include daub.css and daub.js via CDN from https://daub.dev. Full component docs at https://daub.dev/llms.txt
